    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered and garage-kept its whole life, so you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You\u2019ve got to see it to believe how clean it is! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
